{"tid":1423951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該你地搞撚清楚 何式凝呢條左膠臭閪從來唔係同路人","createTime":"2019-08-06T15:08:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T19:35:18.000Z","uid":25240,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a9e7010d606849a9c35a7149be37260c6d6539fd","tid":1423951,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:08:49.000Z","msg":"不割席 不篤灰係同前線義士講<br />\n並唔係對何式凝呢條當義士係數字 既臭閪講<br />\n點解會話佢當義士係「數字」<br />\n因為對佢黎講 7x 個手足被狗拉左對佢黎只係一個數字<br />\n呢班手足 係警署受咩對待/ 會被狗charge 咩 / 會否留案底 佢係唔會理<br />\n呢條臭閪唯一在乎既係佢既社運CV <br />\n<br />\n第二, 佢作為活動搞手 7x個手足出事佢難辭其究<br />\n但睇下佢fb 篇回應 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係連半句sorry 都冇</span></span><br />\n最後仲要扮晒委屈咁有咩攻擊佢頂晒 唔好其他人<br />\n<br />\n累撚左7x 個手足仲要拉人落水幫自己擋 <br />\n一句sorry 唔係好過份呀??<br />\nFYI, 2012 舊登有人搞過「唱蝗團」 <br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">最後效果出黎真係幾柒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n但至少位巴打肯出黎承擔返個責任<br />\n何式凝呢? <br />\n<blockquote> 在此，我希望大家如果要罵左膠，針對我就好了，不要向其他左膠、女性、和理非開炮，一人做事一人當。運動需要團結，希望大家可以不篤灰，不割席，不分化。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7e339998fbd01517896b540bd9be2c907686e968","tid":1423951,"uid":64884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:09:24.000Z","msg":"啱呀屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9466c099eedaf5de873c1d47fef1a12ffb04bbd","tid":1423951,"uid":46966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:10:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尋日想掉鳩佢 但扔唔中"},{"pid":"af00f7af3d16b8e1474858768ac48a106b381184","tid":1423951,"uid":124859,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:13:44.000Z","msg":"左膠一向係敵人"},{"pid":"4be15e228666f5c2c94a89762b59ec5bc57d975d","tid":1423951,"uid":25240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:15:01.000Z","msg":"補充多少少<br />\n點解會話呢條左膠臭閪食人血饅頭?<br />\n大家一齊睇左佢2015年4月講過咩先<br />\n<br />\n我們在分域碼頭路與告士打道出口，一直徘徊，下午兩三點，有人在拾到的紙牌寫上「慢駛」，然後舉起。駕駛者看見了，竟又真的將車速減慢，人群拍掌。有一刻路面汽車流量較少，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">機會稍縱即逝，我們毫不猶疑衝出了馬路，沒想過身後原來有數百人跟著。車都被截停了</span></span>，告士打道給佔領了。當場的人像是心底有種默契，那種解放的舒暢與感動，無法言喻。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/83O2k6o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F83O2k6o.jpg&h=3894412f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10153164976625306&amp;set=a.10151330900170306.535392.664820305&amp;type=1&amp;fref=nf&amp;pnref=story\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10153164976625306%26set%3Da.10151330900170306.535392.664820305%26type%3D1%26fref%3Dnf%26pnref%3Dstory&d=I5RPnmyQkmy%2BYB%2FsDyc%2Bv8VJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=0d0c0527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10153164976625306&amp;set=a.10151330900170306.535392.664820305&amp;type=1&amp;fref=nf&amp;pnref=story</a><br />\n<br />\n一年都唔洗已經改歷史話自己帶頭衝<br />\n想話佢唔係食人血饅頭都唔得啦<br />\n<br />\n前線用血用前途捱棍捱催淚彈 <br />\n條臭閪一句唔該就收割晒D 光環"},{"pid":"fd2eff5337e82f3e24f39daf3f0fd160bc848776","tid":1423951,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af00f7af3d16b8e1474858768ac48a106b381184","tid":1423951,"uid":124859,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:13:44.000Z","msg":"左膠一向係敵人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:15:57.000Z","msg":"見到隔離po 有幾隻洗地狗話「同路人」<br />\n心諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢幾撚時係同路人"},{"pid":"357a063aa1315298e7e59f89b251e5b7dd75fbcf","tid":1423951,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:18:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d1c4e3b4bc51e3d150177f62bcea93f24cf6b3","tid":1423951,"uid":110653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:20:00.000Z","msg":"幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4920bb9628e82c1f38ca661fdea847b5677fd57","tid":1423951,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:21:52.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52963ed1fd5507d2c9441b56ef45769f539f3ef8","tid":1423951,"uid":43804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:43:36.000Z","msg":"201x年：我，何式凝，仆出一條新街<br />\n2019年：我，何式凝，仆出76條新街（不過唔撚關我事）"},{"pid":"f5766f16b9ed765ad16506b35d4bd8c3c7a9d575","tid":1423951,"uid":281180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:23:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"596800f846335b315aa790c5985fad2613915220","tid":1423951,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:35:18.000Z","msg":"天水圍差館外叫人坐低搏黑警唔敢拉 , 啱啱721白衣人事件過左無耐就唔記得左天元警區係全香港最仆街嘅警區"}]}